Wednesday, March 12, 1997

MERIT DOCKET

96-2473. State ex rel. Semenchuk v. Turner.

Madison App. No. CA96-08-033. Sua sponte, cause dismissed as moot.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., concur. Pfeifer, J., dissents and would reverse on the merits.
